"{\"uid\": \"theepochtimes.com-world-rachel-gunn-breaks-silence-on-olympic-breakdance-controversy-5706647\", \"text\": \"Australian Olympic break-dancer Rachael Gunn has addressed her critics in the wake of her controversial performance in Paris.  Gunn, who performs as Raygun, represented Australia in the Olympic break-dancing debut, but her playful moves including dancing like a kangaroo led to criticism and widespread online memes.\"}"